The DSTF is established as a Task Force under the European Union Strategy for the Danube Region (EUSDR) Prioritiy Area 6 (PA06, Biodiversity).&#xd;
The DSTF is an observer to the International Commission for the Protection of the Danube River (ICPDR)&#xd;
The DSTF participates an observer in meetings of the Steering Group of Priority Area 6 (Biodiversity) of the EU Strategy for the Danube River (EUSDR).&#xd;
The DSTF has a Memorandum of Understanding on cooperation with the World Sturgeon Conservation Society.
